---
title: Chorizo and Mushroom Pasta with creamy pesto sauce
description: Did you know that linguine means "little tongues" in Italian? A fitting name seeing as this family-friendly recipe is designed to delight the tastebuds of those both young and old.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221007_R03_W48_IE_IEXCFQP0031-1_KB_Main_remove_the_lardons_edit_high-9cef694e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ie/recipecards/card/64ba569da7c1f8a1e13be1a5.pdf
